                            p
                                | Each class is charged by hour. One hour is&nbsp;
                                strong £4 for members
                                | &nbsp;and&nbsp;
                                strong £6 for non-members.
                                | &nbsp;We offer further discounts to our members who want to commit to dance.
                        .item
                            h3 Membership (Imperial College Students)
                            p
                                | Imperial College students and Union members can become members of Dance Soc by signing up online&nbsp;
                                strong
                                    a(href="https://www.imperialcollegeunion.org/shop/club-society-project-products/dance-products") here
                                | . Once you've done that, bring a copy of your confirmation email to any class (on smartphone or otherwise), and we will give you a membership card which allows you to get 33% off all classes, and even more if you bulk buy! Don't forget to always carry your card with you.
                        .item
                            h3 Membership (Others)
                            p
                                | Other Further or Higher Education students, as well as members of Imperial College staff or ex-students will need the following:&nbsp;
                                strong Imperial College Union Membership AND IC Dance Club Membership
                                | . Instructions how to buy Imperial College Union Membership can be found&nbsp;
                                strong
                                    a(here="https://www.imperialcollegeunion.org/your-union/how-were-run/membership") here
                                | . Once you've bought Union Membership, you will need to buy Club Membership, which can be done online&nbsp;
                                strong
                                    a(href="https://www.imperialcollegeunion.org/shop/club-society-project-products/dance-products") here
                                | . Note that without membership you can only attend scheduled lessons and cannt use pracice space
                        .item
                            h3 Free lessons
                            p.

                                To get you hooked to dance we offer free taster sessions or free classes with membership since we know the best way to get you started is to get you dancing! The best way to hear about any deals we have is to join our mailing list. You can do that here mailing list subscription.
